00:08:40.820 --> 00:08:42.580 align:middle line:90%
And it just felt weird.

00:08:42.580 --> 00:08:45.850 align:middle line:84%
And again, because I really
had a taste of it once

00:08:45.850 --> 00:08:48.910 align:middle line:84%
and my mom was around,
I thought, well--

00:08:48.910 --> 00:08:53.445 align:middle line:84%
this time I was at a dorm
at Griffith Uni in Brisbane,

00:08:53.445 --> 00:08:55.820 align:middle line:84%
and I thought, well, this time
no one's going to be home.

00:08:55.820 --> 00:08:56.590 align:middle line:90%
No one's going to save me.

00:08:56.590 --> 00:08:57.580 align:middle line:90%
This is going to be it.

00:08:57.580 --> 00:09:00.250 align:middle line:84%
But somehow someone
found me again

00:09:00.250 --> 00:09:03.610 align:middle line:84%
