me to go because I've

00:09:09.400 --> 00:09:12.960 align:middle line:84%
got this great mission
that I'm living right now.

00:09:12.960 --> 00:09:15.610 align:middle line:84%
So that's probably
why I didn't go then

00:09:15.610 --> 00:09:17.050 align:middle line:90%
no matter how hard I tried.

00:09:17.050 --> 00:09:21.520 align:middle line:84%
>> You know what's also
interesting is is what

00:09:21.520 --> 00:09:23.900 align:middle line:90%
I've read of your story.

00:09:23.900 --> 00:09:29.170 align:middle line:84%
It's as if-- it was as if
there was a changing moment.

00:09:29.170 --> 00:09:32.900 align:middle line:84%
But for you the changing
moment was very, very clear.

00:09:32.900 --> 00:09:35.170 align:middle line:84%
And this is as if
it was just one day

00:09:35.170 --> 00:09:37.253 align:middle line:84%
