going to live this life.

00:09:37.253 --> 00:09:38.053 align:middle line:90%
>> Sure.

00:09:38.053 --> 00:09:39.880 align:middle line:84%
>> Was it that kind
of black and white?

00:09:39.880 --> 00:09:44.350 align:middle line:84%
>> It seems that way probably
because when I wrote my book I

00:09:44.350 --> 00:09:45.470 align:middle line:90%
