00:10:04.450 --> 00:10:07.492 align:middle line:84%
And another mistake happens
and learn from this one.

00:10:07.492 --> 00:10:08.950 align:middle line:84%
I haven't done this
mistake before.

00:10:08.950 --> 00:10:11.080 align:middle line:84%
And this one, I've got
to learn from this.

00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:13.430 align:middle line:90%
So, no, it wasn't immediate.

00:10:13.430 --> 00:10:19.780 align:middle line:84%
Although, three-- around three
years ago, I was with this man

00:10:19.780 --> 00:10:23.200 align:middle line:90%
that wasn't a nice guy at all.

00:10:23.200 --> 00:10:27.160 align:middle line:84%
And at that time, that was kind
of like the moment when I said,

00:10:27.160 --> 00:10:31.960 align:middle line:84%
