in to meth use for five months.

00:10:31.960 --> 00:10:34.450 align:middle line:84%
And I already had the
charity built by then.

00:10:34.450 --> 00:10:37.960 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, my god, how can
I be your solution to addiction?

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:40.870 align:middle line:84%
And the reason why
that happened was I

00:10:40.870 --> 00:10:44.870 align:middle line:84%
was in a very good
relationship but it fell apart.

00:10:44.870 --> 00:10:49.220 align:middle line:84%
And he, being the pastor's
son, came into my life.

00:10:49.220 --> 00:10:52.100 align:middle line:84%
And he was using meth
and he was injecting me.

00:10:52.100 --> 00:10:55.150 align:middle line:84%
And also-- he knew my
history because we--

00:10:55.150 --> 00:10:57.400 align:middle line:84%
I knew him when I
was 19 years old.

00:10:57.400 --> 00:10:59.830 align:middle line:84%
And he knew that if
he could inject me,

00:10:59.830 --> 00:11:02.220 align:middle line:84%
then I'll be back
in my old ways.

00:11:02.220 --> 00:11:03.020 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:11:03.020 --> 00:11:08.500 align:middle line:84%
So-- yeah, after that time
when I fell and I went back

00:11:08.500 --> 00:11:11.680 align:middle line:84%
