ward in the Philippines,

00:11:11.680 --> 00:11:14.820 align:middle line:84%
and then I came to Australia,
also went in in Australia.

00:11:14.820 --> 00:11:16.780 align:middle line:90%
I'm like, wow, 10 times.

00:11:16.780 --> 00:11:18.880 align:middle line:90%
