the pivotal moment

00:11:24.910 --> 00:11:29.045 align:middle line:84%
where I took the right turn and
it was right from there on in.

00:11:29.045 --> 00:11:30.840 align:middle line:84%
>> So you met a monk
here in Australia.

00:11:30.840 --> 00:11:31.650 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:11:31.650 --> 00:11:32.890 align:middle line:90%
Yes, yes, yes.

00:11:32.890 --> 00:11:36.670 align:middle line:84%
