get me back into what

00:11:47.080 --> 00:11:48.520 align:middle line:90%
they were trying to do.

00:11:48.520 --> 00:11:50.540 align:middle line:84%
And I approached a
friend and I said,

00:11:50.540 --> 00:11:52.060 align:middle line:84%
