00:12:01.690 --> 00:12:03.920 align:middle line:90%
Maybe he can help me out.

00:12:03.920 --> 00:12:05.980 align:middle line:90%
And so she did.

00:12:05.980 --> 00:12:11.200 align:middle line:84%
