a pretty immediate connection.

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:13.360 align:middle line:84%
And we knew that there
was something there.

00:12:13.360 --> 00:12:16.480 align:middle line:84%
But obviously, I
was too traumatized.

00:12:16.480 --> 00:12:19.450 align:middle line:84%
