goals, spiritual goals.

00:12:28.690 --> 00:12:31.450 align:middle line:84%
>> And so what did
transpire with the monk?

00:12:31.450 --> 00:12:37.330 align:middle line:84%
>> What happened was he helped
me through that moment where

00:12:37.330 --> 00:12:39.610 align:middle line:90%
all these people were after me.

00:12:39.610 --> 00:12:41.980 align:middle line:90%
He trained me body wise.

00:12:41.980 --> 00:12:46.810 align:middle line:84%
So he taught me Qigong, which is
a breathing exercise, Tai Chi.

00:12:46.810 --> 00:12:50.350 align:middle line:84%
And, yeah, it's just pretty
much training every day.

00:12:50.350 --> 00:12:52.360 align:middle line:84%
Because he said if
your body is good,

00:12:52.360 --> 00:12:54.040 align:middle line:84%
if you can put down
a person that's

00:12:54.040 --> 00:12:57.700 align:middle line:84%
trying to-- like self-defense,
if someone's trying to come

00:12:57.700 --> 00:12:59.680 align:middle line:84%
at you from behind or
there's people with guns,

00:12:59.680 --> 00:13:01.160 align:middle line:90%
this is what you do.

00:13:01.160 --> 00:13:03.640 align:middle line:84%
And I started training
my body in that way.

00:13:03.640 --> 00:13:06.760 align:middle line:84%
And of course, he taught
me stillness, as well.

00:13:06.760 --> 00:13:10.450 align:middle line:84%
So with the stillness practices
and the Kung Fu practices

00:13:10.450 --> 00:13:15.190 align:middle line:84%
