Chi, and the constant spiritual

00:13:15.190 --> 00:13:18.037 align:middle line:84%
insights that he
would impart upon me--

00:13:18.037 --> 00:13:19.120 align:middle line:90%
because we lived together.

00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:21.010 align:middle line:90%
It was like a 24/7--

00:13:21.010 --> 00:13:25.210 align:middle line:84%
having the Dalai Lama beside you
and asking him all the deepest

00:13:25.210 --> 00:13:26.530 align:middle line:90%
questions in the world.

00:13:26.530 --> 00:13:30.480 align:middle line:84%
Having that really opened
my mind and my heart

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:33.775 align:middle line:84%
and got me on the
road to healing.

00:13:33.775 --> 00:13:35.200 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow.

00:13:35.200 --> 00:13:36.220 align:middle line:90%
Wow, it's amazing.

00:13:36.220 --> 00:13:38.500 align:middle line:90%
>> It's a happy ending.

00:13:38.500 --> 00:13:42.370 align:middle line:84%
>> And this is the beauty of
the sharing is with so many

00:13:42.370 --> 00:13:45.520 align:middle line:84%
